reviewText: There was no data to play on the DVD and possible phishing scam to obtain my debit card information

I do have to admit that at first I didn't purchase this item simply becase of the lack of subtitles and absolutly uncensored however not only was the delivery of this item one of the fastest I have ever gotten from amazon shipping but the all out appearance of the hentai as well as the style were very impressive. I can't wait to see the other episodes.

It was a decent product. It was delivered in a great timely manner, in great condition.  The movie overall is decent, there is sadly some censorship and the dialogue makes sense if you understand Chinese (or is it japanese...meh)  Regardless as far as hentai is concerned it is a decent pick.  A little short though, and not to mention the story kinda skips around..
